title: Going to the JPL Open House? Read this first - Redlands Daily Facts
text:
PASADENA >> This weekend, the NASA Jet Propulsion Laboratory is opening it's usually sealed-shut doors for the general public with the annual JPL Open House . The two-day event is a chance to see some of the coolest things JPL makes, like a model of the Mars Science Laboratory, JPL's machine shop and the Microdevices lab.
 Redlands Daily Facts.
